This is my new deatrun map. Its quite different than any deathrunmap you ever saw

- every new round the path is complete random
- 3 T spawns
- 45 ct spawns
- high res textures

#### How to play Terrorist!!!

- Cts run acros the path like standart deathrun
- Terrorists move on the grid above the creation area
- When a trap is created. It creates a spell circle on the grid which can be used to activate the trap
- Traps can be used only 1 time

Traplist:
------------------

1. Bhop blocks
2. Eruption
3. Fire Pillar
4. Flare Crystal
5. Lava Trap

Special Things
------------------

1. Altar of glory: Random things will happen when pressing +use nearby

Minigames:
------------------

1. ATM only easy

##### Notes

- there are only 5 traps that get created so far. More will come
- this verion is about to test, if servers can handle such maps
- future versions may have up to 50 different traps

##### IMPORTANT!!!

- Post suggestions especially trap suggestions.
- Report bugs/improvements

- Nade tiles
- more traps
- Bossfight (creation percentage will be ultra low)

This map was created from scratch solely by Corn Ibulus. Questions / concerns go to him (me.)

This map's idea was based off Icepick's (Icepick66) Death_Run.

This FPSB account is thanks to Newborn King (or ingame †ÎK† Ñėẅbörn K¡ng{MG}.)

Overview: The counter-terrorists have captured a few terrorists, and have decided to have some fun with them in a closed facility full of sadistic deathtraps.

Objective: COUNTER-TERRORISTS - The terrorists are out to get you, and your only defense is a series of traps designed to kill anyone and everyone. You will need to work together to the best extent choosing who works what obstacle at what time. If you fail, and a terrorist makes it to the end, you will have to scramble and form an alliance to take down the monster with an smg using only knives and strategy.

TERRORISTS - Those pesky counter-terrorists took you from your life only to watch you die in ways pleasing to them. Time to get revenge, but first you will need to dodge traps using your l33t ninja skills you claim to have. If you prove yourself worthy and an adept runner, you will be granted an smg, which you will then use to take down the counter-terrorists. However, make your shots count, because it will be embarrasing if a counter-terrorist lands a blow on you with a knife...

Gameplay: The run is TIMED, and after a minute each platform will sink into the ground.

Thanks to all who helped me along with this map. Also thanks to Icepick for the amazing idea. I hope everyone enjoys this map as much as me and my friends do.

Special thanks to:
Tp|Loller Dan (idea for the button platforms)
3z (beta test host)
FAJ (blender trap idea)
Zein (stair trap idea)

**UPDATE**

Made it easier and added HDR for improved visuals.

I would like to thank half-evil for giving me this wonderful idea. First of all this isnt a normal deathrun map. This map requires autobalance because Ct's and T's race to get to the end first. In the beginging there are 2 teleports for each side to work with buttons.The map is mirrored so its equal and not unbalanced for each team. If everyone on both sides dies the button pushers get killed so there isn't a stalemate waiting for the time to run out. This map is also quite difficult and requires some skill. Its possible to beat just hard.I highly suggest testing on a server because it won't make sence doing by yourself.
Some features of map:
-buttons cant be hogged by the same person every round(random)
-interesting traps. shoop de woop,rick roll'd to death,slide like dodgeing,xc at end.(not too hard), and other challenging traps

My first map.

It is a relatively basic deathrun map, nothing too fancy, run in a straight line etc etc.

No buttons can be spammed, but be warned they have a 20sec reset time, so don't wait around.

If the CTs complete the map, both they and the Ts are teleported to a jump room, where they have to race to a final teleporter. From here there are 3 choices. Have fun checking them out.

Included in this map are 2 secrets at the end, nothing special, just something nice for the CTs.

I understand there are some problems with this map, including bad FPS at times, and will eventually work on a v2 of it, but that is not my primary focus at the moment.

#####Dr. Pain's Facility

The evil Dr.Pain has captured you in his sadistic facility. You, the CTs, need to find a way out and survive the big bloodlusting traps and fight Dr.Pain in 6 different ways. You decide how you fight him, maybe play some grenade tennis against him? Or maybe just a simple soccer game with a bomb attached to the loser? Or maybe the classic way that is locked away somewhere in the map? 

<hr>

- Comic Style Custom textures

- 6 different minigames to fight the evil doc:
1. Scout Map (test your aim with the scout sniper rifle)
2. HE-Tennis (throwing grnades at each other was never such fun!)
3. Bunny Hop (hop like a little cute bunny to the middle of the map but don't look down!)
4. Soccer (play soccer against Dr.Pain, goal twice and a collar bomb around his neck will go off! I don't think I have to tell you what happens if he goals twice...) -Coming soon-
4. Shooting Range (welcome to the shooting range cowboy! - choose your gun and shoot at the targets (the terrorists!) to win)
6. Knife Zone (you think you're the best with the knife? prove it!)

7. Secret Classic Mode (Can you find where it is hidden? It might be right in front of you!)

- 2 difficulties (hard and normal, the terrorists have to push a button at their spawn to active the easy mode. easy mode is recommend when there are less than 8 players playing on the server) -Coming soon-

- 22 deadly traps (15 normal triggable traps and 7 automatic traps)

<hr>
